snippet.title: The Book Mage
snippet.description:
Obsessive reader and constant writer just shouting into the void about book stuff. Fantasy, grimdark, gothic, and occasionally there will be dragons.

Writing, vlogs, book hauls, reviews, literary opinions and dumb book stuff

📚 Half Booktube, half Authortube 🖋️

I sometimes go by Teal online. Feel free to say hi & recommend your favourite book!
